                                        the Virgin.</item>
                                    <item n="2">
                                        <locus from="161v" to="162v">161v-162v</locus>: A prayer to
                                        the Virgin: <q xml:lang="nl">van onse vrouwe.</q>
                                    </item>
                                    <item n="3">
                                        <locus from="232v" to="232v">232v</locus>: <q xml:lang="nl">voer eem cruce</q>.</item>
                                    <item n="3">
                                        <locus from="235v:9" to="240v">235v:9-240v</locus>: Later
                                        fifteenth century additions, in the same hand as <q xml:lang="nl">voer eem cruce</q> on f. 232v.</item>
                                </list>
                            </p>
                        </additions>
